com.google.enterprise.connector.spi
Class ValueType

java.lang.Object
  com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.ValueType
public class ValueType
extends java.lang.Object

An enumeration of the possible value types in a repository. Note:

  • There is only one integer type: LONG
  • There is only one floating point type: DOUBLE
  • The BINARY or STRING types may be used for content
